Friends this is Eddie’s second Christmas with us.😭Let’s share so he can be seen and find his perfect family!❤️

Eddie is kind and gentle with everyone he meets. 

Eddie is thoughtful and calm and wants nothing more than to be in the same space as his humans. 

Eddie is house trained, loves his crate, walks great on a lead, and can be fully trusted alone in the home.

Eddie is an easy, loving dog who wants nothing more than a family to cherish him.❤️

Eddie deserves a family to call his own. 

Please, help us find Eddie his family. He is our longest resident rescue pup and he is simply wonderful. He will make an amazing companion to the humans who finally SEE him and are lucky enough to adopt him. Eddie is not a difficult dog - he has simply been overlooked and we cannot understand why. Come and meet him. Get to know him. We know you’ll fall in love with Eddie the way we have.🐶

If you would like to know more about Eddie, please email adopt@iswmp.org. To adopt Eddie, please fill out an app via
 the Linktree in our bio.
 
HUGE thanks to @monikafelicesmith for taking the time to promote adoption and help Eddie finds his forever home.❤️
